## Filter

| Item | Frequency | Confidence | Disposition |
|------|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| <item> | <N times> | high / medium / low | strong candidate / candidate / hold / contested |

Apply the thresholds from [`docs/core-practices/evolution/delta-extraction.md`](../evolution/delta-extraction.md):

- 2+ independent dreams → strong candidate (ships in this batch)
- 1 dream + matching ERRATA → candidate (ships if reasoning aligns)
- 1 dream, no ERRATA → hold (carries to next batch's Inputs)
- contradictory → contested (preserved, not picked)

